Quick thing to get something out for ChCh so
folks can tweet (and hopefully, soon, 'txt') to say
they need help at a given location, or have an offer
of help

All about letting them find each other by map, list, or other means

some mockups here:
http://www.flickr.com/photos/utunga/sets/72157625993146931/

data available at 
http://chchneeds.org.nz/cdb/_utils